  <text>
    <body><div type="letter">
      <p>Please send me the Check.</p>
      <p>Dearest W. I hope you are not vexed; but I rather feared the high wind on the Downs; &amp; the hour too being an especially inconvenient one to me.</p>
      <p>Pray let me have a line from you. Bird is dispirited altogether. It is not one of her bright days.--</p>
      <p>Tomorrow I will certainly come, in good time.--</p>
      <p>Pray-- a line.--</p>
    </div></body>
